[l] Trump blockiert den Kauf von Qualcomm durch Broadcom. Das waere die groesste Fusion der Geschichte im Tech-Sektor geworden mit einem Kaufpreis von 117 Milliarden Dollar. Begruendung:"There is credible evidence that leads me to believe that Broadcom Ltd.," by acquiring Qualcomm, "might take action that threatens to impair the national security of the United States," Trump said in the order released Monday evening in Washington.National Security!
